sec.p:
To analyze the data set of 90 genes, we developed a script for R frame work to perform a pipeline for filtering and processing data from different sources; the steps are:
data mining analysis on COSMIC and DisGeNET database;
functional profiling using the “g:Profiler” web-based toolset;
discovering for drug-gene interactions on DGIdb;
data retrieving of all publications from NCBI-PubMed about the filtered dataset;
gene alteration association and co-expression correlation analysis on cBioPortal database;
interaction network analysis with GeneMANIA.
